{"tid":2413974,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新一代MC！《人氣歌謠》將由IZ*ONE安兪真＆NCT成燦＆Treasure志焄接棒主持","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T06:41:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ba48aff0e47f37aa0a530422946198b357cb3393","tid":2413974,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_956edc6f9d94ae1429edecc9c3adcd91/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-19/133766-897373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_956edc6f9d94ae1429edecc9c3adcd91%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-19%2F133766-897373.jpg&h=08d443bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如此多才多藝又擁有高顏值的新組合，已經讓人感到非常期待了呢～<br />\n<br />\n總是為所有KPOP粉絲帶來最精彩、好看音樂舞台的SBS《人氣歌謠》，每一代的主持人也都非常受到大家關注，也都是粉絲非常關心的，而18號製作組方面就表示，新的主持群將會由IZ*ONE的安兪真、NCT的成燦以及Treasure的志焄接任！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/official_izone/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fofficial_izone%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69EzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=27faa909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/official_izone/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n從2019年10月20號開始主持的NCT的在玹、APRIL的娜恩還有MONSTA X的玟赫，三人的好默契大家都非常喜歡，不過三人也將於2月28號退位，主持最後一次的《人氣歌謠》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nct/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnct%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69EzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=8aed53d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/nct/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n而3月開始就會由安兪真、成燦、志焄成為新的主持群，到時候會帶來什麼樣的申告式舞台，三人的互動又會是怎麼樣的模式，已經讓人開始期待了，喜歡的粉絲們，也不要錯過每週日播出的《人氣歌謠》囉～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yg_treasure_official/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyg_treasure_official%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69EzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=c9462568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yg_treasure_official/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n(封圖來源：IG@official_izone、IG@nct、IG@g_treasure_official)"},{"pid":"1025a92e0575b52afdae20906ed94136d75e2281","tid":2413974,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612454688d67a18f1a517cc9ee40c859570ba7c1","tid":2413974,"uid":80047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:45:16.000Z","msg":"我女友"},{"pid":"dfa41eccdbcb5f0a985dc69752ee4f6512062f77","tid":2413974,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"屌你樓主今日唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0532cbb80da47e646fc2f935f6f00c059fbe280","tid":2413974,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"真真....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1802d1bc45248037b9ea02667a240218f6f15b","tid":2413974,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa41eccdbcb5f0a985dc69752ee4f6512062f77","tid":2413974,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"屌你樓主今日唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi